data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!!    Welcome to Poinciana, Florida! With its sunny skies and wonderful community, this area is the perfect place to raise a family.    This delightful two-story home, located in the heart of Poinciana, is sure to be ideal for anyone looking for a lovely place of their own. Boasting four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms, this home features a spacious and bright living area, perfect for entertainers. Unveiling a large kitchen and dinette area, it promises flawless family breakfasts and plenty of storage space for all your cooking needs. With a charming front porch and a nice sized lot, you can take advantage of all that is required when it comes to outdoor activities.    On top of that, this residence is situated conveniently close to a community clubhouse, making it easy to relax and unwind.     Take advantage of this amazing opportunity. Schedule a tour today.
